Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:26.44,JoJo-MainTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,1)}JoJo's {\c&H2E0FB2&}Bizarre Adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:26.44,JoJo-MainTitle2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,1)}Stardust Crusaders
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:44.07,JoJo-EpTitle,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(626,425)}Episode 3: The Curse of DIO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:44.77,JoJo-top,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:46.63,JoJo-main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,He's not going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:49.01,JoJo-main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,He'll die in the next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.32,JoJo-top,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:56.42,JoJo-Location,blah,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,459)\b0\fs18}This story is fiction. The characters, groups, places, laws, and names \Nused in this program have no connection to any existing in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:58.70,JoJo-top,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Look. The reason that this \Nman swore loyalty to DIO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:00.76,JoJo-main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,and came to kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:02.78,JoJo-main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:06.48,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,What is that spider-like growth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:10.06,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,You said that's the reason he swore loyalty to DIO?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:13.12,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,That is a flesh bud, formed from DIO's own cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:15.57,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It connects to his brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:21.85,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,This tiny little flesh bud was implanted in his brain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.53,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,to influence his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:27.67,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that flesh bud is a controller
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:29.37,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,that draws forth certain feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.10,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Charisma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.87,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings that make\N soldiers want to obey dictators!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:38.76,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings that make true\N believers follow cult leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:42.76,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This young man admired\N DIO and swore loyalty to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.25,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,DIO is a charismatic figure,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:48.70,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,which means he can sway others
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.25,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with his overwhelming powers of attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:56.40,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He used that to order this young man,\N called Kakyoin, to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.12,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,So operate on him and remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:59.88,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The brain is very delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.07,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If he were to move while we were extracting it,\N we could inflict brain damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:06.76,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Jojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:11.07,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,The following happened four months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.30,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,in Cairo, Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:17.13,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I met DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.87,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I am a fortune teller by trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.66,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a shop in a souk called Khan el-Khalili.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.72,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It was the night of the full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:31.54,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:40.86,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,stood quietly on the stairs that\N led up to my shop's second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:45.37,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,His cold gaze felt as if it was\N trying to stealthily pierce my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.53,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,His golden hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.72,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,his near-transparent alabaster skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:52.86,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,and his strange sensuality made\N it hard to believe he was a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:57.01,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I had heard about him from\N Mr. Joestar, so I knew immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:04:00.66,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,that he was DIO, back from the Atlantic's depths!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:06.01,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that you have powers \Nthat ordinary people don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:11.97,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be grateful if you could show them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:17.98,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that I found him truly terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:23.10,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,His words brought such peace to my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.20,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,They had a dangerous sweetness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:28.20,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why he was terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:31.36,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Avdol...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.23,JoJo-Stab,,0000,0000,0000,,Auuuugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.62,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I ran for my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.12,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't dare think of fighting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:46.21,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I was very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:48.75,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Because I had heard about \NDIO and realized it was him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.94,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to immediately \Njump out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:55.99,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew the labyrinthine souk below like the \Nback of my hand, so I was able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:05:00.04,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I would have \Nended up like this young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:02.69,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,made into one of his\N followers through a flesh bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:07.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You would have died a few years later, \Nyour brain completely devoured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.33,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Died?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:11.09,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.33,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.59,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,isn't dead yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.29,JoJo-Bam2,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(126,0)}Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.98,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pull it out using my Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.26,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.75,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.69,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pull it out without harming his brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:33.27,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,My Stand moves with such precision \Nthat it can grasp even a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.89,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! That flesh bud is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.86,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize why part of\N the flesh bud is outside of his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.61,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's why not even the\N best surgeon could extract it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.07,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.17,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,The flesh bud stabbed him with a tentacle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.78,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! Let go, Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.68,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It will try to enter the brain of \Nanyone who tries to extract it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:56.71,JoJo-main,kakyoin,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:01.25,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, Kakyoin.\N If I fail, your brain is done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:11.09,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, Jojo! It's gone up to your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.64,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Avdol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:15.29,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,My grandson is quite the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:18.56,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's entered his body, \Nand yet he's completely calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.86,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't even trembling. Nor is his Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:26.19,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He moves with more precision \Nand strength than I anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:32.99,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:40.54,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Overdrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:49.80,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:54.81,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.93,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you risk your life to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:07.60,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:12.03,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:24.53,JoJo-internal/narrator,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Mama sees right through you, Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.80,JoJo-FirstAid,sign,0000,0000,0000,,First Aid Kit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.23,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,And done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.88,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.95,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.97,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.56,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Stay the night tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.92,JoJo-overlap,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.60,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, please get his futon ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.72,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:45.24,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even liked the\N idea of sleeping on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:48.61,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly, replace the futon\N in my room with a real bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.55,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, you're in Japan,\N so please just get used to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.45,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the Japanese way of doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:56.70,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and call me "Seiko."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.53,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:02.21,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Holly comes from the word "Holy," \Nwhich is "Seinaru" in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:05.36,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,So all my friends call me "Seiko."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.49,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:09.63,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Holly" is the wonderful name I gave you mys—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.18,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't call me "Seiko" \Nfrom now on, I won't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:12.93,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:15.13,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt, Kakyoin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:15.89,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.89,JoJo-top,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.16,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.35,JoJo-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Kakyoin, take off your uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.04,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:20.89,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.41,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.61,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.84,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly! Hey, Holly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.80,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:42.43,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look. These are Jotaro's pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.39,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Where are mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:48.55,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The size is just right, but I can't wear these!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:50.38,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:56.74,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have to call her "Seiko" \Nor she won't come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:09:02.64,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,No, my daughter is Holly.\N Holly! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:08.57,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely going to go to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:12.19,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.97,JoJo-flashback,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Here, a goodbye kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:16.85,JoJo-flashback,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Smooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:19.98,JoJo-internal/narrator,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,That's usually how it plays out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:55.43,JoJo-Rumble2,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Menacing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.73,JoJo-Bam,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(212,0)}Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:01.74,JoJo-main,Avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Ms...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:02.91,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.31,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Holly! Ms. Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.84,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a really high fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:10.81,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Is she sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:16.43,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,This is... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.76,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:23.99,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.35,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It's intangible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:27.75,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:31.14,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,A Stand has manifested \Nfrom Ms. Holly, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.99,JoJo-Eyecatch3,sign top,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(794,0)}Hermit Purple
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.99,JoJo-Eyecatch2,sign bottom,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(960,0)}Joseph Joestar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:41.89,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Holly has a Stand, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:47.54,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,B-But this high fever... \NThe Stand is causing her harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:51.96,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,We thought that only Jojo and Mr. Joestar\N were being affected by DIO's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:55.13,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,and were relieved that Ms. Holly was unaffected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.56,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,No, we merely wanted to be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.52,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way she could be unaffected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:03.39,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who has the blood of\N the Joestar family in their veins
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:06.14,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,should be affected by DIO.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:07.22,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:12.81,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Stands are controlled by a person's mental strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:15.48,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and move with their fighting instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:18.86,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Holly is very gentle and peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.83,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,She therefore lacks the\N strength to withstand DIO's curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:24.87,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,She has no power to move her Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:30.16,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,That's why her Stand is moving\N against her and harming her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:34.67,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good at all. At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:37.06,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,She'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:38.92,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:45.88,JoJo-Rumble2,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Menacing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.89,JoJo-top,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,A S-Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.14,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.05,JoJo-Smash2,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(166,0)}Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:09.53,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This... This is the one thing I feared most!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:13.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,M-My daughter finally has a Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:18.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she didn't have \Nthe power to withstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:25.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she didn't have the power \Nto deny the curse from DIO's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.48,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me how we should deal with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.48,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.13,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:47.53,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We need to kill DIO and lift the curse!\N That's all we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:50.04,JoJo-Bam,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(445,0)}Bam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.41,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:56.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I try,\N he hides in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:59.25,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,In every spirit photo I take, \Nthe background is darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:03.86,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot find out where he \Nis with my spirit photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:09.41,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,We've used various means to analyze them, \Nbut with this darkness, it always failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:12.68,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me that in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:16.81,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to find out where
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.55,JoJo-Grab,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(374,0)}Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.33,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,that darkness or whatever is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.95,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see something in the space behind DIO?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.16,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,My Stand is able to move with
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:36.09,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,such accuracy that it could\Nextract a flesh bud from his brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:39.01,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and with such precision that it can grasp a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.42,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have him sketch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.09,JoJo-Swish1,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(231,0)}Whoosh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.10,JoJo-Whoosh,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:57.31,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,A fly! A fly was in that space!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.82,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But a fly won't help us at all—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:00.56,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.43,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this fly before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.27,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.93,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Jojo, do you have an encyclopedia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.40,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a library.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.32,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.34,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll go investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.57,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.48,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:22.29,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Just rest. Jotaro, get some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.81,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.73,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm a little busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:47.74,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really possible for your own Stand to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:53.16,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It is. In the past, I have seen \Nmany people suffer that fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.59,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's just her back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:15:00.01,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,but eventually that Stand,\N growing like a fern,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:03.59,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,will slowly bind Ms. Holly's entire body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:07.23,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,She will suffer high fevers and various illnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:10.98,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,fall into a coma from which she'll never awaken,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.02,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:16.43,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,A normal human
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.33,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,would die of something unseen and unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:21.86,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and no skilled doctor would \Nbe able to treat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:27.70,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,No one, not you nor I, \Ncan do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.53,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,But there is still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:35.87,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It will take fifty days for \Nher to reach that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.77,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,We will find and defeat DIO before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.25,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,If we are able to destroy\N the connection to DIO's Stand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.74,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we can save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:49.88,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:53.09,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I wonder what's wrong with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.26,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I took fever and passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:56.26,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:57.89,JoJo-top,holly,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:16:01.94,JoJo-internal/narrator,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't realized what happened, \Nsince it's coming from her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:04.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me quite the scare, Holly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:08.09,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Come now. You've got to\N brush your teeth now that you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:10.06,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "ahh."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:10.06,JoJo-overlap,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.57,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to wash your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:17.08,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair is a mess, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:19.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll take care of your nails...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:22.45,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:22.45,JoJo-overlap,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:28.63,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, help me change my underwear, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.92,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding! It was a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.89,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, what do you want \Nto eat for dinner, Jotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:36.89,JoJo-overlap,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.10,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! Just stay in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:46.65,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm saying that you shouldn't do \Nanything until your fever goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:49.53,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:53.30,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.29,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:01.91,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,You're all so nice when I'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.86,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes having a cold isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:10.52,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,H-Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:14.48,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She lost consciousness again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.99,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,She's acting cheerful, but she's burning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.60,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The way she acted confirms it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:28.76,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Though she hasn't said anything,\N my daughter is aware of her Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:33.72,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,She was actually trying to hide her Stand from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:39.03,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,She was trying not to worry us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:42.80,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's what kind of person my daughter is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:46.62,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar, I've found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.04,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,That fly is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:55.11,JoJo-Nile,sign top,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(398,1209)}Nile
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:55.11,JoJo-Fly,sign middle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(398,1209)}Nile Ue Ue Fly (Male)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:52.41,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.33,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Nile Ue Ue Fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:57.31,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It dwells only within the Nile River Basin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:59.96,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,The ones with the stripes \Non their legs are known
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:02.39,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,as Aswan Ue Ue Flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.71,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Egypt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.43,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,And we've narrowed it\N down to the Aswan area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:07.76,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,DIO is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.12,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,So it is Egypt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.60,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.67,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:17.93,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,The flesh bud was planted in \Nmy brain three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:22.79,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,When my family was on vacation in \NEgypt visiting the Nile, I met DIO.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.97,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,You were in Egypt, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:28.43,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that, for some reason, \NDIO doesn't want to leave Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:31.16,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.21,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.92,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Go with us? Why would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.43,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:45.43,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure why I suddenly \Nwant to join you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.87,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I've regained my senses because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:52.94,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:02.88,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly... we'll save you, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.20,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.26,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.27,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:14.26,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You just take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:22.45,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Jojo's mother, Ms. Holly, is a woman \Nwho can calm the hearts of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.30,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,People feel at ease when she is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:28.03,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,This may sound awkward,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:31.80,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I were to fall in love, I'd like\N it to be with someone like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:33.98,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel like I have to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:38.53,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd want to see her happy, kind smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:40.20,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:45.20,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time. We're leaving immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:55.30,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,They're doctors from the Speedwagon\N Foundation. We can trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.65,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,They will take care of Holly around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:05.78,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Jojo, before we leave, since I am a \Nfortune teller, I shall name your Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:06.64,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.39,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,With the cards of fate, the Tarot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:12.39,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Choose a card blindly and it shall be decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.36,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,This will suggest your fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.98,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as suggest your Stand's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.07,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,The Star! The Star card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.74,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall name your Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.91,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Star Platinum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.77,JoJo-Names1,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(209,1)}Jotaro Kujo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:34.98,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro Kujo. Stand name: Star Platinum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:37.84,JoJo-Names1,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro Kujo                                     Star Platinum
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:37.84,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Powers: Precise movements \Nand splendid strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.88,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph Joestar. Stand name: Hermit Purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:42.84,JoJo-Names2,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(216,160)}Joseph Joestar
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.84,JoJo-Names3,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(216,160)}Hermit Purple
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:42.80,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Power: Spirit photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:46.88,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Mohammed Avdol. Stand name: Magician's Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:48.34,JoJo-Names3,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(166,o)}Mohammed Avdol
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:48.59,JoJo-Names4,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(211,0)}Magician's Red
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:48.61,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Powers: Fire and heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:52.63,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Noriaki Kakyoin.\N Stand name: Hierophant Green!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:55.89,JoJo-Names5,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(211,0)}Noriaki Kakyoin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:55.89,JoJo-Names6,nar,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,0)}Hierophant Green
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:55.90,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Powers: Long distance \Nmanipulation and Emerald Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.82,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.63,JoJo-Bam3,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(207,0)}Bam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:02.99,JoJo-top,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:22:59.76,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,As I anticipated...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:03.59,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,They have figured out my location.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.99,0:23:07.70,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come here to Egypt?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:12.12,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph and Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.25,0:23:15.50,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He saw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.50,0:23:18.38,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely felt DIO looking at us just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:19.42,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:20.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:26.57,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The next Stand user may \Nalready be on this plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:36.97,JoJo-Preview,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:38.28,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We've already found the next Stand user!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.28,0:23:41.01,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! It's faster than Star Platinum!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:42.10,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:44.30,JoJo-main,someone,0000,0000,0000,,It writhes in pain when torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.30,0:23:46.67,JoJo-main,girls,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... He's so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.67,0:23:49.99,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me. Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:49.99,JoJo-NextTitle,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:49.99,JoJo-NextTitle2,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tower of Grey
